{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_M_SawRefire}}
'''A_M_SawRefire'''<br>
(no parameters)<br>

If the calling actor has no target, or the target is dead, or outside of melee range, the calling actor jumps to its next frame.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|ScriptedMarine}} and derived classes.

